29#include <sys/cdefs.h>
30#ifndef lint
31__RCSID("$NetBSD: print-msnlb.c,v 1.3 2017/02/05 04:05:05 spz Exp $");
32#endif
33
34/* \summary: MS Network Load Balancing's (NLB) heartbeat printer */
35
36#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
37#include "config.h"
38#endif
39
40#include <netdissect-stdinc.h>
41
42#include "netdissect.h"
43#include "addrtoname.h"
44#include "extract.h"
45
46struct msnlb_heartbeat_pkt {
47 uint32_t unknown1;
48 uint32_t unknown2;
49 uint32_t host_prio; /* little-endian */
50 uint32_t virtual_ip;
51 uint32_t host_ip;
52 /* the protocol is undocumented so we ignore the rest */
53};
54
55void
56msnlb_print(netdissect_options *ndo, const u_char *bp)
57{
58 const struct msnlb_heartbeat_pkt *hb;
59
60 hb = (const struct msnlb_heartbeat_pkt *)bp;
61 ND_TCHECK(*hb);
62
63 ND_PRINT((ndo, "MS NLB heartbeat, host priority: %u,",
64 EXTRACT_LE_32BITS(&(hb->host_prio))));
65 ND_PRINT((ndo, " cluster IP: %s,", ipaddr_string(ndo, &(hb->virtual_ip))));
66 ND_PRINT((ndo, " host IP: %s", ipaddr_string(ndo, &(hb->host_ip))));
67 return;
68trunc:
69 ND_PRINT((ndo, "[|MS NLB]"));
70}
